{"tid":1472122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正式向無良心既食肆/店鋪宣戰（第一波）","createTime":"2019-08-14T13:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T01:46:38.000Z","uid":26840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8670d7937ca48856ef4596b7c81a188f1e74da1c","tid":1472122,"uid":26840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:00:22.000Z","msg":"作為一個有公民責任既良心市民，遇到無良心既食肆，一定要盡公民責任。<br />\n<br />\n一般食肆，為左做生意都會有咁多檯放咁多檯，甚至放出店舖營業範圍，放出路面街道。<br />\n<br />\n跟據「食物業規例」，持牌食物業處所範圍外非法擴展食肆經營範圍，食環署會按實際情況引用《食物業規例》（第132X章）第34C條（在圖則劃定地方的以外地方經營食物業）檢控有關食肆持牌人，或引用第31(1)(b)條（適用於非持牌人士在食肆核准範圍以外經營）作出檢控。<br />\n<br />\n當扣滿一定分數，有關食肆會被停牌七天、十四天、吊銷牌照，呢個唔係重點，想知詳細自己google下，重點係係係係係係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">點先可以有人去跟進</span></span></strong>!?<br />\n<br />\n最簡單既方法係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1823</span></span></strong>，電話/網上/APPS 全部都得<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.1823.gov.hk%2Fbig5%2F&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXJ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=5a02fd55\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/</a><br />\n<strong>(匿名完全無問題，可以選擇唔公開個人資料，甚至唔需要留資料，只需要留個聯絡方式收回覆)</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">方法如下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只用你幾十秒</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n良心市民只需講出以下內容:-<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n「xxx <span style=\"color: purple;\">(食肆名)</span>」於xx月xx日非法擴充營業，阻礙街道，請食環署馬上跟進。<br />\n<br />\n地址：xxxxxxxxxx</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nP.S. <br />\n(1) 每日都違法就每日盡市民責任<br />\n(2) 如果用APPS, 就係地圖點埋個地點<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果食店無良到無牌都照開，注意係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無牌營業</span></span>! 你無聽錯，係有好多鋪頭都係咁! 咁大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要</span></span></strong>話比食環署知邊間咁衰無牌仲營業緊🤭<br />\n<br />\n引用《食物業規例》（第132X章）第31條(1)<br />\n31.食物業的發牌事宜<br />\n(1)除第33C條另有規定外，除非根據並按照署長根據本規例所批出的牌照，否則任何人不得經營或安排、准許或容受他人經營以下任何一種食物業 &mdash;&mdash;  <br />\n(a)任何食物製造廠；或  <br />\n(b)任何食肆；或<br />\n(ba)任何工廠食堂；或  <br />\n(c)任何燒味及鹵味店；或  <br />\n(d)任何新鮮糧食店；或<br />\n(e)任何凍房；或  <br />\n(f)任何綜合食物店。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以係呢到check下間食肆有冇牌:-<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/licensing/licence-foodPremises-rest.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Flicensing%2Flicence-foodPremises-rest.html&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXJ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=3b376daf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/licensing/licence-foodPremises-rest.html</a><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">如果唔係食肆</span></span></strong>，普通鋪頭如果擺野出曬界，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">都係屬於非法擴展營業範圍</span></span></strong>:-<br />\n<br />\n如店鋪非法擴展營業範圍以致構成無牌販賣罪行，食環署會根據《公眾衛生及市政條例》（第132章）第83B條（在街道上無牌販賣）執法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">建議大家</span></span></strong>用email/apps方式1823，聯絡留email，因為咁樣大家可以隨時email查詢。等食環回覆後，亦可以書面清晰知道佢跟進左d咩，到底有冇扣到分等等。<br />\n<br />\n法例就仲有好多，大家可以詳細睇下:-<br />\n<br />\n第132X章 《食物業規例》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap132X!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap132X%21zh-Hant-HK&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXJ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=c064b979\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap132X!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山!香港加油! 大家加油!"},{"pid":"83fdec765cbdaf3965ab3933dc1740c4c38bd90f","tid":1472122,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8e51570fdad9f99cbee244ced1c4a912b834fc3","tid":1472122,"uid":26840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28afb5209ffdbd08bec1ed5799e33ade058535dd","tid":1472122,"uid":292821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2047541bdc60c6aeeff8cf353bd03b8a10ee27c9","tid":1472122,"uid":74182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMcgcbN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMcgcbN.jpg&h=0852afc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又一間"}]}